item.title: Mingeford365 Podcast 5
item.description: The boys are back once again with the hotly-anticipated new podcast. The people demanded more banter and that is what they have got. Minge and Runyak shoot the shit about Pizza, Nazis, Porn, Joe Kinnear and the Crystal Maze. Also it's a chance to catch up with Quincy and listen to some 'interesting' music, as well as the airing of a message from a celebrity who is furious over being lampooned. If that wasn't enough, there is a super special treat for all MingeFans - Hear it all EXCLUSIVELY on the Mingeca5t. Sign up to the forum at http://www.mingeford365.co.uk/forum

item.description: After extensive delays due to IRL problems, the 6th episode of the adventures of Mingeford and Runyak is finally here. Featuring a breakdown of how Mingeford spends his life (and how he's lost touch with reality), a SHOCKING revealtion about Runyak's youth, and a brand new interactive feature. All this, plus celebrity hate, and the usual lampooning shittery. The sound is a little bit poo in parts, but think it's sorted now so don't complain. Brilliantly edited by Alf Ramsay's Porno Dungeon, if you only download one Christmas podcast this year, make it this one! Sign up to the forum at http://www.mingeford365.co.uk/forum

item.description: Huge robot christ. Mingeford had to do some actual work after christmas, and coupled with the forum being down almost constantly, this is the fist effort of 2009.
